OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud increasing from the
OL,6,Fnorthwest this morning bringing some
OL,7,Fpatchy rain. Becoming mainly dry and
OL,8,Fmuch brighter, with plenty of sunny
OL,9,Fspells during the afternoon. Remaining
OL,10,Fcooler than of later, even in the
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry start to the evening
OL,14,Fwith clear spells. Showers returning
OL,15,Fthrough the night which could become
OL,16,Fheavy at times during the early
OL,17,Fmorning. Most places staying frost
OL,18,Ffree.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
