OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,6,Fblustery showers, some of the showers
OL,7,Fheavy with the added risk of hail in
OL,8,Fplaces. Chilly, with temperatures
OL,9,Fbelow average. Windy for many.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FStaying unsettled on Thursday with
OL,13,Fsome showery rain, and brisk winds.
OL,14,FDrier and brighter on Friday and
OL,15,FSaturday, with winds easing.
OL,16,FTemperatures staying below average for
OL,17,Fthe time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
